{
  "id": "6993df2e9730fd95788a8f5c",
  "title": "使うツールに思考が引っ張られる仮説",
  "created": 1771298607,
  "updated": 1771301239,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6993df2e9730fd95788a8f5c",
      "text": "使うツールに思考が引っ張られる仮説",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533c9c",
      "text": "from [2026/02/17]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533c9d",
      "text": "使うツールに思考が引っ張られる仮説[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298610
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533c9e",
      "text": " テキスト(文章）ベースだと、脳内がテキスト出力モードになる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533c9f",
      "text": " マインドマップ(GUI)だったり、作画ツールだったり、手書きメモだったり",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533ca0",
      "text": " 人によっては絵画やイラスト、音楽とかもありそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e2ae000000000071e63a",
      "text": " 音声入力でのテキスト化も、キーボードを叩いてのテキスト化と違ってきそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771299503,
      "updated": 1771299525
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e4190000000000c8c871",
      "text": " [Claude Code]のようなAIに書かせる、も、ツールのバリエーションになる、、かも？？",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771299865,
      "updated": 1771299894
    },
    {
      "id": "6993df2f0000000000533ca1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771298607,
      "updated": 1771298607
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e02100000000005eac41",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771298849,
      "updated": 1771298852
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e14100000000004b6e66",
      "text": "\t[ネオ・ウォーフ仮説][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771299138,
      "updated": 1771299264
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e02400000000005eac43",
      "text": " 　[サピア・ウォーフの仮説]の発展形として[ダグラス・エンゲルバート]が1962年[Augmenting  human  intellect:  A  conceptual  framework]でこう書いている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771298853,
      "updated": 1771299156
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e13d00000000004b6e64",
      "text": "  　>We offer the following hypothesis, which is related to the Whorfian hypothesis: Both the language used by a culture, and the capability for effective intellectual activity are directly affected during their evolution by the means by which individuals control the external manipulation of symbols. (For identification, we will refer to this as the [Neo-Whorfian hypothesis].)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771299134,
      "updated": 1771299156
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e13e00000000004b6e65",
      "text": "  \"ある文化で使用される言語と、効果的に知的活動する能力は、その発達の過程において、個人がシンボルの外部操作をコントロールする手段によって直接影響を受ける\"(西尾訳)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771299134,
      "updated": 1771299197
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e02400000000005eac42",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/nishio/Augmenting Human Intellect: A Conceptual Framework]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771298852,
      "updated": 1771299211
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e19c00000000004b6e68",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/nishio/ネオ・ウォーフ仮説]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771299229,
      "updated": 1771299229
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e292000000000071e639",
      "text": "\t\t\tへぇへぇ! [taktamur.icon][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771299475,
      "updated": 1771301106
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e18b00000000004b6e67",
      "text": "\t\t\t[コンピュータのように人を扱う例]もそうなのかな[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771299211,
      "updated": 1771301220
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e9630000000000b5df89",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tつまりプログラミング言語という手段の影響を大きく受けてる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771301220,
      "updated": 1771301239
    },
    {
      "id": "6993e9530000000000b5df88",
